Hardest part for me was getting the Velium furs.  They are soloable...pet kite if you have a horse or can get Spirit of Eagle.  I think straight up nuke/pet heal would work too, but i didn't really try.  They hit for up 170s, but dont summon.  Kill the elephants and brontos as I'm pretty sure they're placeholders.  But finding them, half the time in the snow, is a pain.  Bring a ranger.  If you're kos to CoV...haha...well bring lots of people and just kill everything I guess.<br>
<br>
